In the above unit test class written with JUnit and AssertJ, the final two assertions fail.

### Netty version

Discovered in `4.1.97.Final`. Checked code of `main` and `4.1` branches and I see the bug is still present there.

### JVM version (e.g. `java -version`)

Discovered in `Temurin-17.0.9+9`, although the bug would present in any Java version.

### OS version (e.g. `uname -a`)

Discovered in `Linux <hostname redacted> 6.1.66-<kernel patch redacted>.x86_64 #1 SMP PREEMPT_DYNAMIC Mon Dec 18 16:29:07 UTC 2023 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux`, although the bug would present in any OS version.
